{"word":"G5034 - τάχος - táchos - takh'-os - + quickly","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">τάχος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">táchos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">takh'-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">+ quickly</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Noun Neuter / பெயர்ச்சொல் (அஃறிணை)</span>"},{"paragraph":"சீக்கிரம் - பால்வேறுபாடற்ற பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"quickly, shortly"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From the same as <a href=\"#/G5036 - ταχύς - tachýs - takh-oos'/5036\">G5036</a>; a <i>brief</i> space (of time), that is, (with <a href=\"#/G1722 - ἐν - en - en/1722\">G1722</a> prefixed) in <i>haste:</i> - + quickly, + shortly, + speedily.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}